            <h1 class="post-title">Watch Code Taking Shape with TDD</h1>
            <section class="post-meta">
                <time class="post-date" datetime="2015-02-01">01 February 2015</time>  on <a href="tag/tdd/index.html">TDD</a>, <a href="tag/refactoring/index.html">Refactoring</a>, <a href="tag/screencasts/index.html">Screencasts</a>, <a href="tag/calculator/index.html">Calculator</a>, <a href="tag/taking-shape/index.html">Taking Shape</a>, <a href="tag/shapeup/index.html">ShapeUp</a>, <a href="tag/iterating-from-the-right-place/index.html">Iterating from the right place</a>
		<a href="screencast-testfirst-tdd-overview.1#disqus_thread">Comments</a>
